    	<div id="box1" class="box-style1"><br/>
        	<h2 class="title"><span>Career Opportunities</span></h2>
				<div class="entry">
					
                    <div class="content_3col_center">
        <p>With continuous growth and innovation, Bradmark offers a work environment that fosters maximum development and achievement of individual and company goals. Each Bradmark employee contributes as an individual while working in high performance teams to attain shared goals.</p>

<p>The Bradmark workplace is comfortable and progressive, with a touch of artistic elegance. Bradmark exceeds industry standards in every area of employee benefits, demonstrating a deep belief that our greatest asset is our people.</p>

<p>Bradmark is always searching for people committed to technical excellence, with development and support skills in Oracle, Sybase, database management, middleware, client/server and HP3000 enviroment.</p>

<p><em><strong>We're committed to providing the premier work environment!</strong></em></p>
<table width="97%" class="contactInfo">
  <tr><td width="25%" class="darkTD">Phone</td><td width="75%">1.800.621.2808</td></tr>
  <tr><td class="darkTD">Fax</td><td>1.713.623.2564</td></tr>
  <tr><td class="darkTD">Email</td><td><a href="mailto:hr@bradmark.com"><strong>hr@bradmark.com</strong></a></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="darkTD">Address</td><td>4265 San Felipe, Suite 700, Houston TX 77027</td></tr>
  
</table>
		  </div>
          <div class="content_3col_right">
          	<h3><em>Please forward your resume via e-mail for one of the following positions</em></h3>
				<div class="content_3col_right_box">
				  

<ul>
<li><strong>R&D - RDBMS Environments</strong>
A programmer with the knowledge of UNIX, NT, C, C++, Oracle, Sybase, and SQL Server</li>

<li><strong>PreSales Product Support</strong>
A technical specialist with the knowledge of UNIX, Oracle, Sybase, and SQL Server</li>

<li><strong>Marketing Associate</strong>
An experienced marketing professional with a knowledge of the software development business.</li>

<li><strong>Sales</strong>
A sales representative with the knowledge of database management.</li>
</ul>
				</div>
